-- Andy Murray Beats David Ferrer in Sony Open Final in Miami
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2013-03-31T18:35:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-31/andy-murray-beats-david-ferrer-in-sony-open-final-in-miami.html
Andy Murray of Britain recovered to
beat  David Ferrer  in three sets in tennis’s Sony Open final in
Miami today.  Murray’s 2-6, 6-4, 7-6 (7-1) victory over the Spaniard
means Murray overtakes Roger Federer to go second in the world
rankings.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  